column5: That is one awesome pike. Great girth on her too! Well done!
Nice! That is a very healthy looking pike. Congrats on your personal best.
Taro never disappoints, the guy knows Lake O pike better than anyone.  Beauty fish and congrats on the 40!!

I started the 2010 Pike season with one goal, and that was to score a 40+ incher and I did!!  Thanks to Taro from "Fish City Tours" who put me on big Pike all day, I tried for 3 years here in Cooks Bay to score a 40 but 36-37inch was all I could do..
that's a beauty pike for sure! congrats
I see a new Avatar in your future... Congrats!
Nice! Taro's got the TO Pike waters figured out!
what a beast !!!! he wanted to be a muskie when he grew up !!!!!!!!
Thanks everybody!!  For three years I roamed the waters in search of the forty, my search has ended..      now for the 50!!!
Awesome pike!!!   WTG & go get 'er LoL
Crap, that's a big fish... safe to assume you weren't in the kayak?
WTG! Didn't know there are 40 inchers near the Toronto Harbour (where I assume you caught that)!
Nice gator for sure Congrats trophypikehunter Thanks for sharing Leechman
